episodes.title: Ep.154 - Most Disturbing Cult of All Time, The Ant Hill Kids Pt. 1
episodes.description: There was a French Canadian named Roch Thériault, and he believed himself to be one of them great men who spoke to God. He also had a proclivity for some very dark and nasty things, leading to the creation of possibly the most disturbing, NSFW cult of ALL TIME: The Ant Hills Kids.
